  "body": "# Bedrock Entity Models\n\nBedrock Entity Models is a mod that allows Bedrock Edition entity models to be used natively in Java Edition.\n\nThis mod is intended to be used alongside resource packs that utilize Bedrock Edition entity models.\n\n![custom model example](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/MmYSmcY6/images/45ebdedd4ce532986751f23e722ba1154d0cfb54.png)\n\n<details>\n<summary>Supported Resource Packs</summary>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th align=\"center\">Icon</th>\n      <th>Name</th>\n      <th>Downloads</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n  <tr><td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1COPjvze/4d3ef8640575d16c07f8706e04327bd211853b68.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"Norse Mythology Mash-up icon\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/norse-mythology-mash-up\">Norse Mythology Mash-up</a></strong></td><td><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/norse-mythology-mash-up?logo=Modrinth&label=Downloads\" /></td></tr>\n  <tr><td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/ohS9Jkb7/b7faed31431b190e56fd7f1d93e3e45e223a175d.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"Super Cute Texture Pack icon\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/super-cute\">Super Cute Texture Pack</a></strong></td><td><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/super-cute?logo=Modrinth&label=Downloads\" /></td></tr>\n  <tr><td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bkDlbAtL/720a4e007a8fd9f960c7d20ffe65e6683db1d86c.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"Pirates of the Caribbean Mash-up icon\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/pirates-of-the-caribbean-mash-up\">Pirates of the Caribbean Mash-up</a></strong></td><td><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/pirates-of-the-caribbean-mash-up?logo=Modrinth&label=Downloads\" /></td></tr>\n  <tr><td><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/1Ee44YG5/d511ee3a7d36c90b76a84a640bf9586995da0f44.png\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"Egyptian Mythology Mash-up icon\" /></td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/egyptian-mythology-mash-up\">Egyptian Mythology Mash-up</a></strong></td><td><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/egyptian-mythology-mash-up?logo=Modrinth&label=Downloads\" /></td></tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n## Features\n\n- **Bedrock Model Loading:** Dynamically parses Bedrock `.geo.json` geometry files and maps them to Java Edition entity model renderers.\n- **Client Entity Definitions:** Supports Bedrock-style `.entity.json` files for configuring models.",
